# Firebase Admin Configuration (Server-side, secret)
# Get these from your Firebase project's service account JSON file.
# IMPORTANT: For the private key, copy the entire string including "-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----"
# and replace all newline characters with `\n` to make it a single line.
FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL=...
FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY=...
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=...

